<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.11.3/font/bootstrap-icons.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link
        href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Playwrite+GB+S:ital,wght@0,100..400;1,100..400&family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0-beta3/css/all.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-S3hDbi3...examplehash...0nNQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:ital,wght@0,100..900;1,100..900&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/modal.css">

    <!-- Tailwind css cdn  -->
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
</head>

<body>
    
    <div class="desktop-message mt-10 mb-20">
        <div class="card1" style="margin: 0;">
            Welcome to Mind-Drive!
            <br>
            This site is best viewed on a mobile device.
        </div>
    </div>
      
    <div class="desktop-message">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-image-container">
                <img src="/images/About.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <p class="card-title">About Page</p>
        </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image-container">
            <img src="/images/Home.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <p class="card-title">Home Page</p>
    </div>
    <div class="card">
        <div class="card-image-container">
            <img src="/images/Chatbot.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <p class="card-title">Chatbot</p>
    </div>
</div>

    
    <div class="content">
        <%- include('../includes/sidebar') %>
            <div class="intro">
                <h2 class="font-bold raleway">Navigate Your Mental Health Journey Here!</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="mood justify-center items-center flex flex-col">
                <h2>How do you feel today?</h2>
                <div>

                    <button class="mood-btn" data-mood="1">
                        <img src="/images/emojis/sad.png" height="45" width="45" alt=""><br>Sad
                    </button>
                    <button class="mood-btn" data-mood="2">
                        <img src="/images/emojis/neutral.png" height="45" width="45" alt=""><br>Neutral
                    </button>
                    <button class="mood-btn" data-mood="3">
                        <img src="/images/emojis/happy.png" height="45" width="45" alt="">
                        <br>Happy
                    </button>
                    <button class="mood-btn" data-mood="4">
                        <img src="https://banner2.cleanpng.com/20240329/uz/transparent-cute-emoji-cartoon-smiley-face-with-tongue-out6606c458a74191.91054447.webp"
                            height="45" width="45" alt="">
                        <br>Joyful
                    </button>
                    <button class="mood-btn" data-mood="5">
                        <img src="/images/emojis/excited.png" height="45" width="45" alt="">
                        <br>Excited
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
                    <span class="loader hidden" id="loader"></span>
                </div>
                <div class="modal hidden" id="mood-modal">
                    <div class="modal">
                        <p class="message" id="moodtext"></p>

                        <div id="get-activity" style="cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline;">
                            Wanna do some activities to cheer up? Click here
                        </div>

                        <div class="options">
                            <button class="btn" id="closebtn">Close</button>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>


            </div>
            <div class="features items-center">

                <h2 class="text-xl my-4 text-center font-bold" style="padding-left: 20px;">Features</h2>

                <div class="anxiety flex flex-col items-center pt-6">
                    <span class="text-xl my-2 font-bold">Anxiety</span>
                    <iframe style="border-radius: 25px; height: 200px; width: 350px " className="rounded-3xl pt-8"
                        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dknTQktH5Z0" title="YouTube video player"
                        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                        referrerPolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowFullScreen></iframe>
                    <p class="feat-p">Learning relaxation techniques can help you with the mental and physical feelings
                        of fear.</p>
                </div>



                <div class="anxiety flex flex-col items-center pt-6">
                    <span class="text-xl my-2 font-bold">Depression</span>
                    <iframe style="border-radius: 25px; height: 200px; width: 350px " className="rounded-3xl pt-8"
                        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/V6ui161NyTg?si=zttsvjc-0EeTIa0d" title="YouTube video player"
                        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                        referrerPolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowFullScreen></iframe>
                    <p class="feat-p">Learning relaxation techniques can ease the mental and physical symptoms of
                        depression.</p>
                </div>


                <div class="anxiety flex flex-col items-center pt-6">
                    <span class="text-xl my-2 font-bold">Stress</span>
                    <iframe style="border-radius: 25px; height: 200px; width: 350px " className="rounded-3xl pt-8"
                        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/xdqNEWb3VfA?si=QQJIoiX89sxXQSCm" title="YouTube video player"
                        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                        referrerPolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowFullScreen></iframe>
                    <p class="feat-p">Practicing relaxation techniques can reduce stress and restore balance in life.
                    </p>
                </div>


                <div class="anxiety flex flex-col items-center pt-6">
                    <span class="text-xl my-2 font-bold">Post-traumatic stress disorder </span>
                    <iframe style="border-radius: 25px; height: 200px; width: 350px " className="rounded-3xl pt-8"
                        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/lwq_KFTiJ78?si=Eh3E6Ba7_HPCEmBy" title="YouTube video player"
                        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share"
                        referrerPolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowFullScreen></iframe>
                    <p class="feat-p">Learning relaxation techniques can help manage symptoms and improve coping with
                        PTSD.</p>
                </div>

                <div class="text-sm items-center justify-center flex flex-col mb-24">
                    Copyright Â© 2024. All rights reserved.
                    <br>Sristy Paul & Pooranjoy Bhattacharya
                </div>

                <%- include('../includes/navbar') %>
</body>
<script src="/js/global.js"></script>

</html>